<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Channel Attribution Report · Centara Hotels</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.js"></script>
<style>
:root {
  --white:   #ffffff;
  --off:     #faf9f7;
  --paper:   #f4f2ee;
  --border:  #e8e4dc;
  --border2: #d4cfc5;
  --text:    #1a1814;
  --text2:   #3d3a34;
  --muted:   #8a8278;
  --muted2:  #b5b0a8;
  --gold:    #c9a96e;
  --gold2:   #a07c40;
  --gold-bg: #fdf8f0;
  --sidebar: 220px;
  --topbar:  52px;
  --font-serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  --font-sans:  'Montserrat', sans-serif;
  --font-mono:  'DM Mono', monospace;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  background: var(--off);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 13px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  min-height: 100vh;
}

/* ── TOP BAR ── */
.topbar {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 200;
  height: var(--topbar);
  background: var(--white);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex; align-items: center;
  padding: 0 2rem 0 calc(var(--sidebar) + 2rem);
  justify-content: space-between;
}
.topbar-left {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
}
.topbar-title {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic;
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 0.3px;
}
.topbar-sep { color: var(--border2); font-size: 12px; }
.topbar-date {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.topbar-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
.topbar-badge {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 9px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border: 1px solid var(--gold);
  color: var(--gold2);
  background: var(--gold-bg);
}

/* ── SIDEBAR ── */
.sidebar {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; bottom: 0; z-index: 201;
  width: var(--sidebar);
  background: var(--white);
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
}
.sidebar-logo {
  padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem 1rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.sidebar-brand {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 17px; font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--text); line-height: 1.2;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.sidebar-brand small {
  display: block;
  font-size: 9px; font-weight: 500;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px;
}
.sidebar-subtitle {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold2); margin-top: 6px;
}

.nav-section {
  padding: 1rem 0 0;
}
.nav-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 8px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted2);
  padding: 0 1.4rem .5rem;
}
.nav-item {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  padding: 8px 1.4rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  border-left: 2px solid transparent;
  transition: background .15s, border-color .15s;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.nav-item:hover { background: var(--off); }
.nav-item.active {
  border-left-color: var(--gold);
  background: var(--gold-bg);
}
.nav-item .ni-icon {
  width: 14px; height: 14px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted);
}
.nav-item.active .ni-icon { color: var(--gold2); }
.nav-item .ni-text {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text2);
  letter-spacing: 0.2px;
}
.nav-item.active .ni-text { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
.nav-item .ni-badge {
  margin-left: auto;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 8px; padding: 1px 6px;
  background: var(--paper); color: var(--muted);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.sidebar-footer {
  margin-top: auto;
  padding: 1rem 1.4rem;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.sidebar-footer p {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 8px; color: var(--muted2);
  letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;
  line-height: 1.8;
}

/* ── MAIN ── */
.main {
  margin-left: var(--sidebar);
  margin-top: var(--topbar);
  flex: 1;
}

/* ── TAB PANELS ── */
.tab-panel { display: none; }
.tab-panel.active { display: block; }

/* ── PAGE HERO ── */
.page-hero {
  background: var(--white);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 2.5rem 2.5rem 2rem;
}
.page-hero-eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 9px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold2); margin-bottom: .8rem;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
}
.page-hero-eyebrow::after { content: ''; width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); }
.page-hero h1 {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
  font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: -0.5px; line-height: 1.15;
  color: var(--text); margin-bottom: .6rem;
}
.page-hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold2); }
.page-hero-sub {
  font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 300;
  max-width: 520px; line-height: 1.8;
}

/* ── STAT STRIP ── */
.stat-strip {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  background: var(--white);
}
.stat-cell {
  flex: 1; min-width: 140px;
  padding: 1.2rem 1.8rem;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.stat-cell:last-child { border-right: none; }
.stat-val {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.stat-lbl {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 9px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted);
}

/* ── SECTION WRAPPER ── */
.section-wrap {
  padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
}
.section-wrap + .section-wrap {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}

/* ── SECTION HEADER ── */
.section-header {
  display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
}
.section-num {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 8px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--muted2);
}
.section-header h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic;
  color: var(--text2); letter-spacing: 0.2px;
}
.section-header p {
  margin-left: auto;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

/* ── KPI ROW ── */
.kpi-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(170px, 1fr));
  gap: 1px; background: var(--border);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.kpi-cell {
  background: var(--white);
  padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem;
  position: relative;
}
.kpi-cell::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 2px; background: var(--gold);
  opacity: 0;
}
.kpi-cell.highlight::before { opacity: 1; }
.kpi-val {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 1.7rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: -0.3px; color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 5px;
}
.kpi-lbl {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 8px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
}
.kpi-sub {
  font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 3px;
  font-weight: 300;
}

/* ── CHART CARD ── */
.chart-card {
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.chart-card-head {
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  padding: .9rem 1.3rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.chart-card-title {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 9px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted);
}
.chart-legend {
  display: flex; gap: 16px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted);
}
.chart-legend span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
.leg-sq { width: 8px; height: 8px; }
.chart-body { padding: 1.2rem; }

/* ── CLASS GRID ── */
.class-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: 1px; background: var(--border);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.class-card {
  background: var(--white);
  padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
}
.class-card-top {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.class-name {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.4;
}
.badge {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 8px; padding: 2px 7px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;
  white-space: nowrap; border: 1px solid;
}
.badge-conv  { color: var(--gold2); border-color: var(--gold); background: var(--gold-bg); }
.badge-ass   { color: var(--muted); border-color: var(--border2); background: var(--paper); }
.badge-dual  { color: var(--text2); border-color: var(--border2); background: var(--off); }
.badge-mod   { color: var(--muted2); border-color: var(--border); background: var(--white); }
.class-stats {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 7px;
}
.class-stats b { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
.class-desc { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.prog-track { height: 1px; background: var(--border); }
.prog-bar   { height: 100%; background: var(--gold); }

/* ── INSIGHTS ── */
.insight-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
  gap: 1px; background: var(--border);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.insight-card {
  background: var(--white);
  padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem;
}
.insight-n {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 8px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold2); margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.insight-card h4 {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic;
  color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 6px; line-height: 1.3;
}
.insight-card p { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.75; }

/* ── TABLE ── */
.table-wrap {
  overflow-x: auto;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  background: var(--white);
}
table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 11px; }
thead th {
  background: var(--paper);
  color: var(--muted);
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 8px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 9px 14px; text-align: left;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); transition: background .1s; }
tbody tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
tbody tr:hover { background: var(--off); }
tbody td { padding: 9px 14px; color: var(--text); font-weight: 400; }
tbody td.mono { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; }
tbody td.muted { color: var(--muted); }
.tpill {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 7px; padding: 2px 6px;
  font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase;
  border: 1px solid var(--border2); color: var(--muted);
  background: var(--paper);
}

/* ── FOOTNOTE STRIP ── */
.insight-strip {
  background: var(--gold-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--gold);
  padding: .9rem 1.3rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.insight-strip p {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 13px; font-style: italic;
  color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.7;
}
.insight-strip strong { font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }

/* ── STATUS ROW ── */
.status-row {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  background: var(--white);
}
.status-item {
  flex: 1; min-width: 130px;
  padding: .9rem 1.1rem;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.status-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
.status-item .s-val {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 3px;
}
.status-item .s-lbl {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
}
.status-item .s-note {
  font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px;
}
.s-gold { color: var(--gold2); }
.s-ok   { color: #4a7c59; }

/* ── FOOTER ── */
.page-footer {
  background: var(--white);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .5rem;
  margin-left: var(--sidebar);
}
.page-footer-l {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; color: var(--muted);
}
.page-footer-r {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 9px; color: var(--muted2); letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.page-footer-r a { color: var(--gold2); text-decoration: none; }

/* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
.reveal {
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px);
  transition: opacity .5s ease, transform .5s ease;
}
.reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  :root { --sidebar: 0px; }
  .sidebar { transform: translateX(-100%); transition: transform .25s; }
  .sidebar.open { transform: none; }
  .topbar { padding-left: 1rem; }
  .page-hero, .section-wrap { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .page-footer { margin-left: 0; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
  .topbar { left: 0; }
  .hamburger { display: flex !important; }
}
.hamburger {
  display: none;
  flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;
  cursor: pointer; padding: 6px;
  background: none; border: none;
}
.hamburger span { width: 18px; height: 1px; background: var(--text); display: block; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- SIDEBAR -->
<aside class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
  <div class="sidebar-logo">
    <div class="sidebar-brand">
      Centara Hotels
      <small>Attribution Report</small>
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar-subtitle">Apr 2026 · All Properties</div>
  </div>

  <nav class="nav-section">
    <div class="nav-label">Sections</div>
    <a class="nav-item active" onclick="showTab('overview',this)">
      <span class="ni-icon">◈</span>
      <span class="ni-text">Overview</span>
    </a>
    <a class="nav-item" onclick="showTab('channels',this)">
      <span class="ni-icon">◎</span>
      <span class="ni-text">Top 10 Channels</span>
    </a>
    <a class="nav-item" onclick="showTab('email',this)">
      <span class="ni-icon">◉</span>
      <span class="ni-text">Email Attribution</span>
      <span class="ni-badge">12</span>
    </a>
    <a class="nav-item" onclick="showTab('insights',this)">
      <span class="ni-icon">◇</span>
      <span class="ni-text">Insights</span>
      <span class="ni-badge">6</span>
    </a>
  </nav>

  <div class="sidebar-footer">
    <p>
      Data period: All paths<br/>
      Currency: THB (1 USD = ฿33.5)<br/>
      Rate: Chart.js attribution<br/>
      Updated: Apr 2026
    </p>
  </div>
</aside>

<!-- TOP BAR -->
<header class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-left">
    <button class="hamburger" onclick="toggleSidebar()">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
    <span class="topbar-title">Channel Attribution &amp; Path Analysis</span>
    <span class="topbar-sep">·</span>
    <span class="topbar-date">Updated 29 Apr 2026</span>
  </div>
  <div class="topbar-right">
    <div class="topbar-badge">Apr 2026</div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- MAIN -->
<main class="main">

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
       TAB: OVERVIEW
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div id="tab-overview" class="tab-panel active">

    <div class="page-hero reveal">
      <div class="page-hero-eyebrow">Key event attribution paths</div>
      <h1>Channel Performance<br/><em>&amp; Attribution</em> Analysis</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-sub">Multi-touch path analysis across all traffic sources — identifying which channels drive last-touch conversions, which assist, and their contribution to revenue in Thai Baht.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="stat-strip reveal">
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-val">฿1.23B<span style="font-size:1rem">+</span></div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Total attributed revenue</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-val">300<span style="font-size:1rem">+</span></div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Unique path combinations</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-val">50<span style="font-size:1rem">+</span></div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Distinct source channels</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-val">1–20</div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Touchpoints per path</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-val">12</div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Email sources tracked</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-wrap reveal">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-num">—</span>
        <h2>At a glance</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="status-row">
        <div class="status-item">
          <div class="s-val s-gold">Google</div>
          <div class="s-lbl">Top converter</div>
          <div class="s-note">Dual role · highest volume</div>
        </div>
        <div class="status-item">
          <div class="s-val s-gold">GHotelAds</div>
          <div class="s-lbl">Top assister</div>
          <div class="s-note">~65% assist ratio</div>
        </div>
        <div class="status-item">
          <div class="s-val s-ok">(direct)</div>
          <div class="s-lbl">Purest closer</div>
          <div class="s-note">&gt;75% last-touch rate</div>
        </div>
        <div class="status-item">
          <div class="s-val">฿33.7M</div>
          <div class="s-lbl">Email top revenue</div>
          <div class="s-note">r.email.myghs.com</div>
        </div>
        <div class="status-item">
          <div class="s-val">6+ days</div>
          <div class="s-lbl">Email avg. to conversion</div>
          <div class="s-note">Long nurture cycle</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="insight-strip">
        <p><strong>Key finding:</strong> Google and Google Hotel Ads together appear in the vast majority of all revenue-generating paths. Direct traffic almost exclusively converts on last touch — a strong loyalty and CRM signal. Social channels (Facebook, Instagram) play a pure awareness role with 7+ day conversion cycles, while Affilired operates as a mid-funnel coupon bridge before customers close elsewhere.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
       TAB: TOP 10 CHANNELS
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div id="tab-channels" class="tab-panel">

    <div class="page-hero reveal">
      <div class="page-hero-eyebrow">Transaction attribution</div>
      <h1>Top 10 <em>Channels</em></h1>
      <p class="page-hero-sub">Last-touch conversions versus assisted touchpoints across all multi-touch attribution paths. Hover bars for assist ratio and totals.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section-wrap reveal">
